{
  "stem": "24614.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we saw this, and we, ha, it was like somebody was bringing in the world to us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We'll finally eat a piece of chicken after a year or so, and we had matzah.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had a pound of matzah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Kroll and my mother-- I don't know if we knew-- but Kroll and my mother knew about a rabbi who was in hiding.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And my mother looked at this pound of matzah and the chicken and she says to us, don't get so happy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Don't put your hopes up because this is not for you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We will eat bread if we have.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But the rabbi will die if he doesn't have matzah, because he's not going to eat anything else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "My mother cooked the chicken, I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she asked Kroll to come at night and take me to the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I went to the rabbi with the chicken and with the pound of matzah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Now, the rabbi lived in a cubicle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There wasn't even room-- I think he slept on the floor too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But he had a little, not oven, those two burners.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hot plate?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like a hot plate?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said to me, he said, now who's going to light the fire?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said to Kroll, light the fire for him, it's small.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's Passover.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He won't-- he's not putting a match.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Kroll says to me, if he doesn't want to do, let him starve.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was Kroll's-- he felt already too much you want.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said to Kroll, I said, you know what, you talk to him, and I'll do it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he talked to him, and I lit the little oven, the flame.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I left the rabbi with a pound of matzah and the chicken.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
